#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
", and feel free\n"
"                        to"
msgstr ""
", ແລະ ຢ່າລັງເລ\n"
"                        ທີ່ຈະ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. Go to the \"Sales\" App and create a new quotation using the main \"New\""
" button on the top left."
msgstr ""
"1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ \"ການຂາຍ\" ແລະ ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໂດຍການໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ \"ໃໝ່\" ຫຼັກຢູ່ເບື້ອງຊ້າຍດ້ານເທິງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Go to the Barcode App, and select \"Operations\"."
msgstr "1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ ບາໂຄດ, ແລະ ເລືອກ \"ການດຳເນີນການ\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Go to the Purchase App."
msgstr "1. ໄປທີ່ແອັບ ການຈັດຊື້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. Point of sale"
msgstr "1. ຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "1. View results"
msgstr "1. ເບິ່ງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. We can now go through your weekly replenishment report to ensure a good "
"supply in your shop. To do so, navigate to the Inventory App &gt; Operations"
" &gt; Replenishment."
msgstr ""
"1. ດຽວນີ້ພວກເຮົາສາມາດກວດເບິ່ງລາຍງານການເຕີມເຕັມສິນຄ້າປະຈຳອາທິດຂອງທ່ານ ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າມີສິນຄ້າພຽງ"
"ພໍໃນຮ້ານ. ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ > ການດຳເນີນການ > ການເຕີມເຕັມສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. Welcome Elise, your favorite customer, she wants to buy the \"Da Vinci "
"Code\"."
msgstr ""
"1. ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ Elise, ລູກຄ້າຄົນໂປດຂອງທ່ານ, ລາວຕ້ອງການຊື້ປຶ້ມ \"Da Vinci Code\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"1. You welcome now Hanna Liseuse, but she has a very specific need. She's "
"looking for \"Media Burn: Ant Farm and the Making of an Image\". You don't "
"have this book in stock, let's order it."
msgstr ""
"1. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານກຳລັງຕ້ອນຮັບ Hanna Liseuse, ແຕ່ລາວມີຄວາມຕ້ອງການທີ່ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງຫຼາຍ. ລາວກຳລັງຊ"
"ອກຫາປຶ້ມ \"Media Burn: Ant Farm and the Making of an Image\". ທ່ານບໍ່ມີປຶ້ມຫົວນີ້ໃນສາງ, "
"ພວກເຮົາລອງມາສັ່ງຊື້ມັນກັນເລີຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. By clicking on the search bar, you can select the \"Weekly "
"replenishment\" filter. It displays every products sold this week and their "
"remaining quantity."
msgstr ""
"2. ໂດຍການຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກຕົວຕອງ \"ການເຕີມເຕັມປະຈຳອາທິດ\". ມັນຈະສະແດງທຸກສິນ"
"ຄ້າທີ່ຂາຍໃນອາທິດນີ້ ແລະ ຈຳນວນທີ່ເຫຼືອຢູ່."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Control your stock"
msgstr "2. ຄວບຄຸມສາງສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Create a new request for quotation, and start adding your products."
msgstr "2. ສ້າງໃບຂໍຄຳສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່, ແລະ ເລີ່ມເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Customer orders"
msgstr "2. ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງລູກຄ້າ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. Elise also wants to buy a 50€ Gift Card for a friend."
msgstr "2. Elise ຍັງຕ້ອງການຊື້ບັດຂອງຂວັນມູນຄ່າ 50€ ໃຫ້ໝູ່ອີກດ້ວຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "2. In \"Receipts\", create a new reception by clicking the \"New\" button."
msgstr "2. ໃນ \"ໃບຮັບເຄື່ອງ\", ສ້າງການຮັບເຄື່ອງໃໝ່ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ໃໝ່\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. Once you've found it on your local books database, go to the sales app and create a new product using its ISBN code : 9781941753354. Define the current distributor in your region by going to the \"Purchase\" tab (use \"My Book\n"
"                Distributor\" for this case)."
msgstr ""
"2. ເມື່ອທ່ານພົບມັນໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນປຶ້ມທ້ອງຖິ່ນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຂາຍ ແລະ ສ້າງສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ໂດຍໃຊ້ລະຫັດ "
"ISBN: 9781941753354. ກຳນົດຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍໃນພາກພື້ນຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໄປທີ່ແຖບ \"ການຈັດຊື້\" (ໃຊ້ \"My "
"Book Distributor\" ສຳລັບກໍລະນີນີ້)."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"2. They want to get an offer for three copies of \"Harry Potter and the "
"Philosophers Stone,\" \"Hidden Life of Trees,\" and \"Sapiens: Brief History"
" of Humankind.\""
msgstr ""
"2. ພວກເຂົາຕ້ອງການຂໍ້ສະເໜີລາຄາສຳລັບປຶ້ມສາມຫົວຄື \"Harry Potter and the Philosophers "
"Stone,\" \"Hidden Life of Trees,\" ແລະ \"Sapiens: Brief History of "
"Humankind.\""

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Choose how much of each you want to buy by entering the value in the \"To"
" Order\" column."
msgstr ""
"3. ເລືອກຈຳນວນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການຊື້ແຕ່ລະຢ່າງໂດຍການປ້ອນຄ່າໃສ່ໃນຖັນ \"ສັ່ງຊື້\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Elise has a customer account; select her using the \"Customer\" button."
msgstr "3. Elise ມີບັນຊີລູກຄ້າຢູ່ແລ້ວ; ໃຫ້ເລືອກລາວໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ \"ລູກຄ້າ\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Institutional customers"
msgstr "3. ລູກຄ້າອົງກອນ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Once your quotation is ready, you can email it or confirm it."
msgstr ""
"3. ເມື່ອໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານພ້ອມແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງອີເມວ ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນມັນໄດ້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. Scan your products. If it does not exist in your database, they will be "
"created with the correct picture, title, and price."
msgstr ""
"3. ສະແກນສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ. ຖ້າມັນບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ, ມັນຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃໝ່ພ້ອມກັບຮູບພາບ, ຊື່ເລື່ອງ, ແລະ ລາຄາ"
"ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "3. Set the quantity in negative value to create a reverted purchase."
msgstr ""
"3. ຕັ້ງຄ່າຈຳນວນເປັນຄ່າລົບເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍການສົ່ງຄືນສິນຄ້າ (ການຈັດຊື້ຍ້ອນກັບ)."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"3. You can now create a new quotation. Type her name in the \"Customer\" "
"field to create a new contact."
msgstr ""
"3. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃໝ່ໄດ້. ພິມຊື່ຂອງລາວໃນຫ້ອງ \"ລູກຄ້າ\" ເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍຊື່ຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ໃໝ່."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Add the product to your quotation by searching for its ISBN. You can "
"directly click on the confirm button to turn your quotation in a Sales "
"Order."
msgstr ""
"4. ເພີ່ມສິນຄ້າເຂົ້າໃນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານໂດຍການຄົ້ນຫາ ISBN ຂອງມັນ. ທ່ານສາມາດຄລິກປຸ່ມຢືນຢັນໄດ້ທັນທີເ"
"ພື່ອປ່ຽນໃບສະເໜີລາຄາໃຫ້ເປັນໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Check the smart buttons, a new delivery has been created, but you need to"
" have all products in stock."
msgstr ""
"4. ກວດເບິ່ງປຸ່ມອັດສະລິຍະ (Smart buttons), ການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງໃໝ່ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນແລ້ວ, ແຕ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງມີສິນຄ້າທຸກຢ່າງ"
"ໃນສາງກ່ອນ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Click then on the \"Order\" button to add it to your purchase orders."
msgstr "4. ຈາກນັ້ນຄລິກປຸ່ມ \"ສັ່ງຊື້\" ເພື່ອເພີ່ມມັນເຂົ້າໃນຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Enter the cost of each new product so you can easily reorder it "
"afterward."
msgstr ""
"4. ປ້ອນຕົ້ນທຶນຂອງສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ແຕ່ລະຢ່າງ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ໄດ້ງ່າຍໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"4. Register Elise's payment. You can now go back to your main dashboard by "
"selecting \"Backend\" in the top-right burger menu."
msgstr ""
"4. ລົງທະບຽນການຊຳລະເງິນຂອງ Elise. ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດກັບຄືນໄປທີ່ໜ້າຫຼັກໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກ "
"\"Backend\" ໃນເມນູຂີດສາມຂີດຢູ່ມຸມຂວາເທິງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "4. Weekly replenishment"
msgstr "4. ການເຕີມເຕັມສິນຄ້າປະຈຳອາທິດ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model:loyalty.reward,description:bookstore.loyalty_reward_2
#: model:product.template,name:bookstore.product_product_17_product_template
msgid "5% on your order"
msgstr "ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ 5% ສຳລັບຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງທ່ານ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "5. Encode new release"
msgstr "5. ບັນທຶກສິນຄ້າອອກໃໝ່"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Go to the Inventory App. A new Replenishment is suggested under "
"Operations &gt; Replenishment."
msgstr ""
"5. ໄປທີ່ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ. ການເຕີມເຕັມສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ຈະຖືກແນະນຳພາຍໃຕ້ ການດຳເນີນການ > ການເຕີມເຕັມສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Navigate to the Purchase App. You can see that all purchase orders have "
"been created and are ready to be sent to your distributors. Enter your "
"purchase orders and send them to your vendors using the Send by Email "
"button."
msgstr ""
"5. ໄປທີ່ແອັບການຈັດຊື້. ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ທັງໝົດໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນແລ້ວ ແລະ ພ້ອມທີ່ຈະສົ່ງໃຫ້ຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍຂອງທ່າ"
"ນ. ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ ແລະ ສົ່ງໃຫ້ຜູ້ຂາຍໂດຍການໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ ສົ່ງທາງອີເມວ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"5. Validate the reception, and this is it! (A purchase order will be "
"automatically created so you can easily reconcile your vendor bills)."
msgstr ""
"5. ກວດສອບການຮັບເຄື່ອງ, ແລະ ສໍາເລັດ! (ຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ທ່ານສາມາດກວດສ"
"ອບຍອດໃບເກັບເງິນຂອງຜູ້ຂາຍໄດ້ງ່າຍ)."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"6. If you select your product and click on \"Order\", a new Purchase Order "
"is created, you can then email it to your distributor and confirm the order "
"placement."
msgstr ""
"6. ຖ້າທ່ານເລືອກສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ຄລິກໃສ່ \"ສັ່ງຊື້\", ຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ໃໝ່ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ, ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາມາດສົ່ງ"
"ອີເມວຫາຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນການສັ່ງຊື້ໄດ້."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "6. Returns"
msgstr "6. ການສົ່ງຄືນ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"7. A few days later, you receive your order from the distributor. Go to the "
"Inventory App on you dashboard, you'll see that a new receipt is ready to be"
" processed. Select it and validate your reception."
msgstr ""
"7. ສອງສາມມື້ຕໍ່ມາ, ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບສິນຄ້າຈາກຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍ. ໃຫ້ໄປທີ່ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າໃນໜ້າຫຼັກ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໃບຮັບເຄື່ອງໃ"
"ໝ່ທີ່ພ້ອມຈະດຳເນີນການ. ເລືອກມັນ ແລະ ກວດສອບການຮັບເຄື່ອງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "7. Monitoring &amp; reporting"
msgstr "7. ການຕິດຕາມ ແລະ ການລາຍງານ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"8. The last product is now in stock, you can go back to your Sales Order and"
" process the delivery by clicking the \"Delivery\" smart button."
msgstr ""
"8. ສິນຄ້າສຸດທ້າຍມີຢູ່ໃນສາງແລ້ວ, ທ່ານສາມາດກັບໄປທີ່ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ ແລະ ດຳເນີນການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກປຸ່ມອັ"
"ດສະລິຍະ \"ການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງ\"."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Barcode App</b>:</font> Use mobile "
"scanners to perform inventory counts and receive new shipments efficiently, "
"reducing manual entry errors."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບບາໂຄດ</b>:</font> ໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງສະແກນມືຖືເພື່ອຈັດການກ"
"ານນັບສາງສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ຮັບສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ຊ່ວຍຫຼຸດຜ່ອນຄວາມຜິດພາດຈາກການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນດ້ວຍມື."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Inventory App</b>: </font>Master your "
"library of titles, using barcode scanning for rapid stock adjustments and "
"managing locations for different genres or sections."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ</b>: </font>ຈັດການລາຍຊື່ປຶ້ມຂອງທ່ານຢ່າງ"
"ມືອາຊີບ, ໂດຍໃຊ້ການສະແກນບາໂຄດເພື່ອປັບປຸງສາງຢ່າງໄວວາ ແລະ ຈັດການສະຖານທີ່ວາງປຶ້ມຕາມປະເພດ ຫຼື ໝວດ"
"ໝູ່ຕ່າງໆ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Invoicing App</b>:</font> Simplify your "
"bookkeeping by tracking daily sales and supplier invoices in one integrated "
"financial system."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບການອອກໃບແຈ້ງໜີ້</b>:</font> ເຮັດໃຫ້ການເຮັດບັນຊີຂ"
"ອງທ່ານງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ ໂດຍການຕິດຕາມການຂາຍປະຈຳວັນ ແລະ ໃບເກັບເງິນຈາກຜູ້ສະໜອງໃນລະບົບການເງິນທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ກັນ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Point of Sale App</b>: </font>Process "
"transactions quickly using barcode scanners to read ISBNs, handling "
"discounts and customer loyalty programs with ease."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ (POS)</b>: </font>ດຳເນີນການຂາຍຢ່າງໄວ"
"ວາໂດຍໃຊ້ເຄື່ອງສະແກນບາໂຄດເພື່ອອ່ານ ISBN, ຈັດການສ່ວນຫຼຸດ ແລະ ລະບົບສະມາຊິກລູກຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Purchase App</b>:</font> Automate "
"replenishment orders based on sales velocity, ensuring you never run out of "
"the latest bestsellers."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້</b>:</font> ສ້າງຄຳສັ່ງເຕີມສິນຄ້າໂດຍອັດຕະ"
"ໂນມັດຕາມຄວາມໄວຂອງການຂາຍ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າປຶ້ມຂາຍດີຈະບໍ່ຂາດສາງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
