#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"ທັງໝົດນີ້ແມ່ນໃຊ້ຟຣີໃນການສະໝັກໃຊ້ປະຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານ; ເຊີນສຳຫຼວດໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ! 🙃"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, you received a new release from one of your distributors. Prepare"
" your scanner and go to the Barcode App."
msgstr ""
"ຄັ້ງນີ້, ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບປຶ້ມອອກໃໝ່ຈາກຜູ້ຈຳໜ່າຍ. ກຽມເຄື່ອງສະແກນຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ພ້ອມ ແລະ ໄປທີ່ແອັບບາໂຄດ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Time to return some unsold products. This works like a reverted purchase "
"order."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງເວລາສົ່ງຄືນສິນຄ້າທີ່ຂາຍບໍ່ອອກ. ສິ່ງນີ້ເຮັດວຽກຄືກັບຄຳສັ່ງຈັດຊື້ທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງຄືນ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model:base.automation,name:bookstore.update_inventory_description
msgid "Update Inventory Description"
msgstr "ອັບເດດລາຍລະອຽດສາງສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model:base.automation,name:bookstore.base_automation_1
msgid "Update supplier info on incoming products"
msgstr "ອັບເດດຂໍ້ມູນຜູ້ສະໜອງໃນສິນຄ້າຂາເຂົ້າ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the internal link button, at the right of the field, to view the new "
"contact record created, and don't forget to add an email address for her to "
"receive notifications. Go back to your quotation using the breadcrump."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມລິ້ງພາຍໃນ, ທາງດ້ານຂວາຂອງຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ, ເພື່ອເບິ່ງບັນທຶກຜູ້ຕິດຕໍ່ໃໝ່ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນ, ແລະ ຢ່າລືມເພີ່ມທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມວເພື່ອ"
"ໃຫ້ລາວໄດ້ຮັບການແຈ້ງເຕືອນ. ກັບຄືນໄປທີ່ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາຂອງທ່ານໂດຍໃຊ້ແຖບ Breadcrumb."

#. module: bookstore
#: model:pos.category,name:bookstore.pos_category_2
msgid "Various"
msgstr "ຫຼາກຫຼາຍ"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:bookstore.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການໄປໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແລ້ວໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ໜ້າຫຼັກ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can also use automated Reordering rules to ensure you will always have "
"your best seller in stock."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ກົດການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນໃໝ່ແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າມີສິນຄ້າຂາຍດີໃນສາງສະເໝີ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can make a down payment using the Point of Sales. To do so, just go back"
" to this app and click on the Quotation/Order button to retreive the Sales "
"Order."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຊຳລະເງິນມັດຈຳໄດ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ຈຸດຂາຍ (POS). ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ພຽງແຕ່ກັບໄປທີ່ແອັບນີ້ ແລະ ຄລິກໃສ່ປຸ່"
"ມ ໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ/ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ ເພື່ອດຶງຂໍ້ມູນໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can now confirm the purchase, validate the delivery using the smart "
"button, and print your delivery slip."
msgstr ""
"ດຽວນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດຢືນຢັນການຈັດຊື້, ກວດສອບການສົ່ງເຄື່ອງໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມອັດສະລິຍະ, ແລະ ພິມໃບສົ່ງເຄື່ອງຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that Elise has a Loyalty Card. The demo Library applies a 5% "
"discount for every 200€ spent. Manage Promotions, and Loyalty programs under"
" Point of Sale &gt; Products. <br/>"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຫັນໄດ້ວ່າ Elise ມີບັດສະມາຊິກ. ຫ້ອງສະໝຸດຕົວຢ່າງນຳໃຊ້ສ່ວນຫຼຸດ 5% ສໍາລັບທຸກໆ 200€ ທີ່ໃຊ້ຈ່າ"
"ຍ. ຈັດການໂປຣໂມຊັນ ແລະ ແຜນງານສະມາຊິກ ພາຍໃຕ້ ຈຸດຂາຍ &gt; ສິນຄ້າ. <br/>"

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້ຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີທີ່ຈະປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວ"
"າມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Bookstore package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢູ່. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ > Industries > ອັບເກຣດແພັກເກດຮ້າ"
"ນຂາຍປຶ້ມຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Bookstore package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your bookstore efficiently."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຫາກໍ່ຕິດຕັ້ງແພັກເກດ Odoo ສຳລັບຮ້ານຂາຍປຶ້ມ. ໂດຍການເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງແອັບທີ່ຈຳເປັນຈຳນວ"
"ນໜຶ່ງເພື່ອໃຫ້ຮ້ານຂາຍປຶ້ມຂອງທ່ານດຳເນີນການໄດ້ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ."

#. module: bookstore
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bookstore.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດປະຕິບັດຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງການເຮັດວຽກຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າງໄວວາດ້"
"ວຍແພັກເກດນີ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ Odoo."

